      "title": "Tense situ at Kandakadu Rehab Centre: One inmate killed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An inmate at the Kandakadu Treatment and Rehabilitation Centre in Polonnaruwa was killed following a tense situation between two groups.",
        "Around a thousand detainees were staying at the Kandakadu rehabilitation Centre which is under the Bureau of Commissioner General Rehabilitation.",
        "It was reported that more than 500 inmates have escaped the Centre amidst the clash.",
        "The Police and the Army have taken steps to control the situation."
